{"tha-ap225:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap225:0.2":"Alambanadayakavagga ","tha-ap225:0.3":"3 Dverataniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap225:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap225:1.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap225:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap225:1.4":"ahutinam patiggaham. ","tha-ap225:2.1":"Mamsapesi maya dinna, ","tha-ap225:2.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap225:2.3":"Sadevakasmim lokasmim, ","tha-ap225:2.4":"issaram karayamaham. ","tha-ap225:3.1":"Imina mamsadanena, ","tha-ap225:3.2":"ratanam nibbattate mama; ","tha-ap225:3.3":"Duveme ratana loke, ","tha-ap225:3.4":"ditthadhammassa pattiya. ","tha-ap225:4.1":"Teham sabbe anubhomi, ","tha-ap225:4.2":"mamsadanassa sattiya; ","tha-ap225:4.3":"Gattanca mudukam mayham, ","tha-ap225:4.4":"panna nipunavedani. ","tha-ap225:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap225:5.2":"yam mamsamadadim tada; ","tha-ap225:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap225:5.4":"mamsadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap225:6.1":"Ito catutthake kappe, ","tha-ap225:6.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap225:6.3":"Maharohitanamo so, ","tha-ap225:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap225:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap225:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap225:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap225:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dverataniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap225:9.1":"Dverataniyattherassapadanam tatiyam. ","tha-ap225:9.2":"Dasamam bhanavaram. "}